  <brief_title>The Effects of Fractional Carbon Dioxide (CO2) Laser Treatment Prior to Wound Closure</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Fractional CO2 Resurfacing Prior to Complex Wound Closure</official_title>
  <sponsors>
